description: Savanna Fox is our Rookie cup champion this season. She is one of the most impressive light weights in the division. She takes on Lea Lexis today. Lea wants so badly to make it to the finals of the light weight championship so she can redeem herself against Darling. Who ever wins today gets the chance to fight Darling for the light weight championship. Extra BTS footage at the end
title: Lea Lexis and Savannah Fox Wrestle Naked and fight for a sex prize
